PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX s223: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.3/Brick#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?zone WHERE {
  # Identify all zone entities (any class whose IRI contains "Zone")
  ?zone a ?zoneClass .
  FILTER regex(str(?zoneClass), "Zone", "i") .

  {
    # ---------------------------------------------------------------
    # Case 1 – the zone has a directly associated property
    # ---------------------------------------------------------------
    ?zone ?directPred ?property .
    ?property a ?propClass .
    FILTER regex(str(?propClass), "Property", "i") .
  } UNION {
    # ---------------------------------------------------------------
    # Case 2 – the zone is linked to a property via a RoomDomainSpace
    #         following any length of connection chain.
    # ---------------------------------------------------------------
    # Walk any number of "hasSpace" / "hasSubSpace" links to a RoomDomainSpace
    ?zone (s223:hasSpace|s223:hasSubSpace)* ?roomSpace .
    ?roomSpace a ?roomSpaceClass .
    FILTER regex(str(?roomSpaceClass), "RoomDomainSpace", "i") .

    # From the RoomDomainSpace follow any number of property‑related links
    ?roomSpace (s223:hasProperty|s223:hasPoint)* ?property .
    ?property a ?propClass2 .
    FILTER regex(str(?propClass2), "Property", "i") .
  }
}
